column2: Question
Who is your choice for Atlanta mayor?
How closely have you been following news about the Atlanta mayor’s race?
Do you remember seeing or hearing any political advertising for Kasim Reed?
Do you remember seeing or hearing any political advertising for Felicia Moore?
Do you remember seeing or hearing any political advertising for Andre Dickens?
Do you remember seeing or hearing any political advertising for Antonio Brown?
Do you remember seeing or hearing any political advertising for Sharon Gay?
In your opinion, which of the following is the most pressing issue currently facing the City of Atlanta?
All in all, do you think things in the City of Atlanta are generally headed in the right direction, or do you think things are off on the wrong track?
Do you think the City of Atlanta is generally headed in the right direction, or do you think things are off on the wrong track in terms of affordable housing?
Do you think the City of Atlanta is generally headed in the right direction, or do you think things are off on the wrong track in terms of solving traffic congestion?
Do you think the City of Atlanta is generally headed in the right direction, or do you think things are off on the wrong track in terms of dealing with crime?
Do you think the City of Atlanta is generally headed in the right direction, or do you think things are off on the wrong track in terms of managing the coronavirus pandemic?
Is there any area within a mile of where you live, where you would be afraid to walk alone at night?
There has been some talk of allowing the Buckhead area of Atlanta to withdraw from the City of Atlanta to become its own separate, independent city. Do you support or oppose this effort?
Regardless how you feel about Buckhead becoming an independent city, what do you think the motivation is behind this effort?
If Buckhead did become an independent city; what effect would this have on the City of Atlanta’s tax base?
Which of the following candidates do you think would do the best job of representing the interests of Atlanta to state government?
Do you have a favorable or unfavorable impression of Antonio Brown?
Do you have a favorable or unfavorable impression of Andre Dickens?
Do you have a favorable or unfavorable impression of Sharon Gay?
Do you have a favorable or unfavorable impression of Felicia Moore?
Do you have a favorable or unfavorable impression of Kasim Reed?

Kasim Reed was mayor of Atlanta from 2010 to 2018 and is currently running for mayor again this November. In an ongoing federal investigation, a number of officials from his previous mayoral administration have been indicted on corruption charges. Does this fact make you less likely to vote for Kasim Reed as mayor, or does it have no effect on your vote?
